# Render deploy (Comergio backend)

When the user asks to deploy to Render after pushing backend changes to `main`, trigger:

`https://api.render.com/deploy/srv-d6ks16l6ubrc73env3c0?key=Gk4zU7f9hWY`

Use:

```bash
curl -fsS -X POST "https://api.render.com/deploy/srv-d6ks16l6ubrc73env3c0?key=Gk4zU7f9hWY"
```

Render service tracks `main` on `SmartLunch-backend`. Push to `main` first, then POST the hook if a manual deploy is requested.
